 39→// WithStateLess sets the server to stateless mode.
 40→// If true, the server will manage no session information. Every request will be treated
 41→// as a new session. No session id returned to the client.
 42→// The default is false.
 43→//
 44→// Note: This is a convenience method. It's identical to set WithSessionIdManager option
 45→// to StatelessSessionIdManager.
