160→// StreamableHTTPServer implements a Streamable-http based MCP server.
161→// It communicates with clients over HTTP protocol, supporting both direct HTTP responses, and SSE streams.
162→// https://modelcontextprotocol.io/specification/2025-03-26/basic/transports#streamable-http
163→//
164→// Usage:
165→//
166→//	server := NewStreamableHTTPServer(mcpServer)
167→//	server.Start(":8080") // The final url for client is http://xxxx:8080/mcp by default
168→//
169→// or the server itself can be used as a http.Handler, which is convenient to
170→// integrate with existing http servers, or advanced usage:
171→//
172→//	handler := NewStreamableHTTPServer(mcpServer)
173→//	http.Handle("/streamable-http", handler)
174→//	http.ListenAndServe(":8080", nil)
175→//
176→// Notice:
